sequenceDiagram
  participant Board as SleepMonitorBoard
  participant Client as board_client.py
  participant PC as PC Server
  participant Act as Humidifier / IR IP

  Board->>Client: sensor_data
  Client->>PC: send sensor_data
  PC-->>Client: sleep_result
  PC-->>Client: control_command
  Client->>Board: apply_control_command(command)
  Board->>Board: validate sample_id / targets / cooldown
  Board->>Act: apply accepted target or skip
  Board-->>Client: control_status
  Client->>PC: send control_status

